tafsir[110]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Mantireede Sifaaji Timmal e Manngu, e Neema fee√±u…ói …óin e suu…óii…ói …óin ko Alla Heeranii Kanko tun, On Tellin…óo Alqur'aana e Jeyaa…óo Makko e Nulaa…óo Makko Muhammadu (yo Alla Juulu e makka O Hisna), O wa…óanaali ndee Alqur'aanaare oo√±agol e selugol Goonga kan."
  18,2,"Ko woni O wa…óii nde focciinde yeddondire e lorre alaa e nder mayre; fii yo o hul…ìinir yeddu…ìe …ìen immorde e Lepte dolnu…óe habbii…óe …ìe ka Alla, o yeetoo gom…óin…ìe …ìen, …ìen golloo…ìe golleeji mo∆¥∆¥u…ói …óin ko weltinta …ìe, wonnde no woodani …ìe mbarjaari mo∆¥∆¥iri, …ìadotaako nde mbarjaari goo."
  18,3,"Ko duumotoo…ìe e nder ndin mbarjaari poomaa, ndi ta∆¥ataa e ma…ì…ìe."
  18,4,"O hul…ìinira Alyahuuda e Annasaara e yoga serkoo…ìe …ìen, …ìen wi'i: ""Alla jogitike …ìi…ó…óo""."
  18,5,"Latanaaki …ìee fefindotoo…ìe ganndal maa…óun dalil e ko …ìe nodditii kon immorde e dammbugol …ìi…ó…óo e Alla. Laatanaaki baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, …ìe …ìe √±entini …ìen kadi e …óun ganndal, no kaani haa fanti ngol konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunndu…óe ma…ì…ìe ko aldaa e huuturo hakkil, …ìe wowlaali si wanaa konngol fenaande, ngol alaa da∆¥∆¥ere, alaa ka ngol …ìaarii."
  18,6,"Bela jo'o an -an Nulaa…óo- a tilfay hoore-maa sabu suno e mette, si …ìe hoolaaki ndee Alqur'aanaare, wota a wa…óu, fawaaki ma fewnugol …ìe, anndu ko fawimaa ko yottinngol."
  18,7,"Menen wadi ko woni kon ka kene leydi ndin e tageefooji ≈ãari mayri, fii yo Men jarbaade…ìe ko hommbo e ma…ìbe …ìurata mo∆¥∆¥innde golle weltinay…óe Alla, ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe kadi …ìurata bonude golle, fii yo Men yo…ìu mokala ko o hanndi kon e mun."
  18,8,"Menen gom…óii Men wattay ko woni kon ka kene leydi ndin e tageefooji mbullaari yeewundi immore e pu…ói, …óun ko …ìaawo re'ugol ngurndan tageefooji wonu…ói …óin e hoore mayri, yo …ìe tasko …óun."
  18,9,"Wota a sikku -ko an yo Nulaa…óo- wonnde fillayee yim…ìe fammeere nde=wimmba ngo, e alluuje ma…ì…ìe, …óen …óe in…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen winndaa e mun no jeyaa e Aayeeje Amen hawnii…óe …óen. Ko woni ko tanaa majje …ìuri hawnaade yeru tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin."
  18,10,"Annditii an yo Nulaa…óo, tuma nde sukaa…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen moolinoo e diina mun kan …ìe fattoyii, …ìe wi'i e nder noddugol ma…ì…ìe ngol Joomi ma…ì…ìe: ""Joomi amen, okku men Hinnayee immorde ka Maa …óun woni haforanaa men bakkatuuji amen, danndaa men ay…ìe e amen, wa…óanaa men fiyaake fergu ngun iwde e keefeeru yaha e gom…óinal feewude faade e laawol Goonga e Peewal."
  18,11,"Refti, …ìaawo yahugol ma…ì…ìe soroya ka fammeere Men wa…ói ka dow noppi ma…ì…ìe wirngallo gaayi nanugol hitooji, Men li…ìi …óoyngol ngol e ma…ì…ìe duu…ìi …óuu…óu…ói."
  18,12,"Refti, …ìaawo …óoyngol ma…ì…ìe juutungol ngol, Men finndini …ìe fii yo Men anndu -Ganndal fen√±inngol- ko honnde e feddeeji poo…óondiray…ói …óin …ói…ói, fii dummunne √±ii…ìugol ma…ì…ìe ka fammeere, …ìuri anndunde emmbere on dummunne."
  18,13,"Menen, Me…óen ∆¥ellintine -ko an yo Nulaa…óo- e kumpital fii ma…ì…ìe e Goonga ka sikke alaa e mu'un, …ìen, ko sagataa…ìe gom…óin…ìe Joomi mun, …ìe golliri doftaare Makko, Men …ìeydani …ìe Fewneede e Tabintineede e hoore Goonga."
  18,14,"Men semmbiniri …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen gom…óinal e tabitugol e maggal, e mu√±anal e dow ferugol ngenndi fii gom…óinal, fewndo …ìe darinoo yeeso lando ngeddo=keefeero on ko …ìe fen√±in…ìe gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe Alla Kanko tun, …ìe wi'ani mo: "" Joomi amen Mo men gom…óini men Rewi On, ko On Jey…óo kammuli …óin e leydi ndin, men rewataa si wonaa Kanko immorde …óin nodditiraa…ói rewatee…óe e hoore fenaande, gom…óii haray men wi'ii -si men rewii tanaa Makko- konngol too√±ungol wo…ó…óitiingol Goonga kan."
  18,15,"Refti yoga ma…ì…ìe ye∆¥∆¥itii e yoga hi…ìe wi'a: ∆Åee yim…ìe amen …ìe jogitike gaanin Alla rewetee…ói hi…ìe rewa…ói, kam…ìe …ìe maraa dalil …ìanngu…óo e dewal ma…ì…ìe ngal, alaa hay e gooto …ìur…óo too√±ude ko foti e on fekkindor…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla dammbugol kafidaa…óo e Makko."
  18,16,"Tuma nde danndi on gaayi yim…ìe mon …ìen, terti…óon ko …ìe rewata kon gaanin Alla, on rewaali si wanaa Alla Kanko tun, fattoyagol ngol ka fammeere fii dogidugol e diina mon kan Joomi mon Senii…óo On hiMo weftana=wertana on immorde e Yurmeende Makko nden ko hiMo reenira on …óun immorde e ay…ìe mon O hiwa on kadi, O niwinana on e fiyaake mon ko hi…óon nafitora …óun, konko lontinanta on e ngurdan…óan hakkunde yim…ìe mon."
  18,17,"∆Åe ja…ìi ko …ìe yamiraa kon, Alla li…ìi …óoyngol e ma…ì…ìe, O reeni …ìe e ga√±o ma…ì…ìe on. A yi'ay -an sutii…óo …ìe- naange ngen si nge ∆¥ellitike ka fu…óirde magge hinge oo√±ora e fammeere ma…ì…ìe nden ka senngo √±aamo naatungo ngon e mayre, si nge wirnike ka mutugol magge nge selirana nde ka senngo nano mayre nge hewtataa nde, kam…ìe hi…ìe e …óowde duumiindi nguli naange ngen tampintaa …ìe, kam…ìe hi…ìe e yaajeende ka fammeere henndu ndu …ìe hatonnjini ndun e mu'un no hewtude …ìe, …óun ko …ìe he…ìi immorde e wernugol …ìe ka fammeere, e li…ìugol …óoyngol e ma…ì…ìe, e oo√±agol naange ngen e ma…ì…ìe, e yaajugol nokkuure ma…ì…ìe nden, e danndugol …ìe bone yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen: Ko jeyaa…óun e kaaweeji Golle Alla tinndin…óe e Katta…óe Makko, kala mo Alla hawrinndini e Laawol Peewal ko on woni feewu…óo e goonga, on Mo o tertii…óun e gaayi maggol O majjini mo, a he…ìantaa mo walloowo mo no hawrinndina mo e Peewal, o fewna mo e maggal; sabu fewnugol ngol ko e Junngo Alla woni, wonaa e juu…óe makko kanko."
  18,18,"A sikkay …ìe -an ndaaroowo …ìe- ko …ìe finu…ìe sabu udditagol gite ma…ì…ìe, ko selli kon kam…ìe ko …ìe …óaanii…ìe, Me…óen waylitira …ìe e nder …óoyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol tumagoo √±aamo, tumagoo kadi nano, fii wata leydi ndin √±aamu …ìalli ma…ì…ìe …óin, rawaandu ma…ì…ìe setodundu ndun e ma…ì…ìe hindu focci koy…óe mayru ka damal fammeere nden, sinno a yaltitiino e ma…ì…ìe yi'u…óaa …ìe a huccitayno e ma…ì…ìe dogaa sabu hulugol …ìe, wonkii maa heewayno kulol ma…ì…ìe."
  18,19,"Ko wano Men wa…óirani …ìe nii, ko Men jantii kon immorde e hawnii…ói Kattan…óe Amen, Men finndini …ìe …ìaawo dummunne juutu…óo fii yo wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe lanndo wo…ì…ìe fii on dummunne mo …ìe …ìooyi …óaanaade e mun, wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe jaabii: ""En √±ii…ìii e nder …óoygol √±allal maa…óun yoga e √±allal."" Wo…ì…ìe e ma…ì…ìe jaabii, o mo fee√±anaali …óun dummunne √±ii…ìugol ma…ì…ìe e …óoyngol: ""Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo dummunne √±ii…ìugol mon ko on …óaanii…ìe, …ìe fawee e Makko ganndal …óun jokkee ko ndaari on kon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii mbuu…ói mon kaalise …óoo ka saare me'en woowaande, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e yim…ìe mayre …ìuri laa…ìude √±aametee …ìuri laa…ìude kadi wonirde, yo o molto ka naatugol saare nden e ka yaltugol nde e ka huuwondiral makko, yo o wonu ∆¥o∆¥u…óo, wata o accu gooto annda fii nokkuure mon nden; sabu ko …óun addata kon immorde e lorra maw…óo."""
  18,20,"Pellet, yim…ìe mon …ìen si …ìe yaltitii e mon …ìe anndii nokku mon, …ìe wariray on fi…óirgol on kaa∆¥e, maa…óun …ìe artira on e laawol ma…ì…ìe …ìoyliingol ngol, ngol ngol wonuno…óon e mu'un ko adii Alla Neeminirde on Peewal faade e Goonga kan, si on artii e maggol on maletaake poomaa, wanaa ka ngurndan aduna wanaa ka laahara kadi, ko woni, on hayray e aduna e laahara hayrere mawnde nden sabu …óalugol moo…óon Diina Goonga ha kan, kan ka Alla Fewni on e mun, artugol moo…óun e ngol laawol …ìuyleengol."
  18,21,"Ko wano Men wa…óirani …ìe nii golleeji hawnii…ói tinndin…ói …óin e Kattan Amen immorde e …óanningol …ìe duu…ìi …óuu…óu…ói, e finndinngol …ìe …ìaawo …óun, Men ∆¥ellintini yim…ìe saare ma…ì…ìe nden fii ma…ì…ìe, fii yo yim…ìe saare ma…ì…ìe nden anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden fii Wallugol gom…óin…ìe …ìen e Immital ngal ko Goonga, pellet Darngal ngal ko arayngal sikke alaa fii maggal. Tuma nde fiyaake yim…ìe fammeere nden huncinoo …ìe maayi yi'unoo…ìe …ìe …ìen luutondiri fii ma…ì…ìe: Ko hon…óun …ìe wa…óata e fiyaake ma…ì…ìe on? Fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: ""Mahee ka dammbugal fammeere ma…ì…ìe maadi wirnayndi …ìe e hiwayndi …ìe, ko Joomi ma…ì…ìe woni Anndu…óo lhaali ma…ì…ìe, alhaali ma…ì…ìe on no holli wonnde no woodani …ìe keerore ka Makko. …ìe konngol mun ja…ìetee …ìen tawa …ìe alaa ganndal e noddaandu sellundu …ìe wi'i: ""Men jogitoto sanne e oo nokku ma…ì…ìe Juulirde fii dewal ka teddinngol …ìe e anndintinnde nokku ma…ì…ìe."
  18,22,"Aray ka wi'a wo…ì…ìe e junpay…ìe …ìen fii fillayee ma…ì…ìe gaayi limoore ma…ì…ìe: ""Kam…ìe ko …ìe tato naya…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun."" Wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe kadi wi'a: ""Kam…ìe ko …ìe nayo njowa…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun, feddeeji …óin …ói…ói kala ko …ìe wi'i kon ko ko hawrondiri e sikke ma…ì…ìe ko aldaa e dalil."" Wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe kadi no wi'a: ""kam…ìe ko …ìe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun."" Maaku -an Nulaa…óo-: ""Ko Joomi an woni Anndu…óo limoore ma…ì…ìe, anndaa limoore ma…ì…ìe si wanaa see…óaa…ìe jeyaa…ìe e …ìen …ìe Alla anndini limoore ma…ì…ìe."" Wata a yeddondir fii limoore ma…ì…ìe, maa tanaa mun e alhaaliiji ma…ì…ìe yim…ìe defte …ìen maa tanaa ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa yeddondiral fee√±ungal ngal luggeendi alaa e mun, …óun woni ra…ì…ìin…óinoraa wahayu tellii…óo on e maa…óa fii fiyaake ma…ì…ìe on, wata a lanndo gooto e ma…ì…ìe e fensitali fii fiyaake ma…ì…ìe, pellet, kam…ìe …ìe anndaa …óun."
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an -an Nulaa…óo- huunde nde faandi…óaa huuwude …óun janngo: Min mi wa…óay ndee huunde jango; sabu an a anndaa yalli a wa…óay nde, maa si heedete hakkunde maa e mayre? dun ko waaju wonanndu ka jul…óo."
  18,24,"Si wonaa yowaa gollugol …óun e Muy…óe Alla, …óun woni maakaa: ""Aray mi huuwa …óun -si Alla Muuyii- janngo, janto Joomi maa ka maakugol maa: ""Si Alla Muuyii -si a yejjetii maakude …óun- Maaku: ""Mi…óo jortii nde Joomi an fewnatan mi ko …ìuri …ìadaade immorde e oo fiyaake Peewal e Kawrindinal."
  18,25,"Yim…ìe fammeere nden √±ii…ìi ka nder fammeere ma…ì…ìe duu…ìi teeme…ó…óe tati e jeenay."
  18,26,"Maaku: -an Nulaa…óo- ko Alla Anndi emmbere ko …ìe woni ka fammeere ma…ì…ìe, gom…óii O humpitii en dummunne wonugol ma…ì…ìe ton, gooto maraa konngol …ìaawo Daalol Makko ngol Senaade wonanii Mo, ko Kanko tun woodani ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ko wirnii kon ka leydi Tagugol e Anndugol, kaawee ko yi'ini Mo O Senike! Kanko hiMo Sutii ka huunde, kaawee ko nanini Mo! Kanko hiMo nana kala huunde. Laatanaaki …ìe gaanin Makko gi…óo mono hikkoo e fiyaake ma…ì…ìe, O tawnaali ka √ëaawoore Makko hay e gooto, ko Kanko tun woni teelir…óo √ëaawoore nden."
  18,27,"Janngu -an Nulaa…óo- gollir ko Alla wahayini kon e maa…óa immorde e Alqur'aana, wattitoowo konngu…ói Makko …óin alaa; sabu kannji ko …ói fow ko …ói Goongu…ói Nun…óu…ói, a he…ìataa gaanin Makko O Senike fattorde=moolorde nde hi…óa fattoo=moolo e mun, wanaa moolortee…óo mo hi…óa moolora …óun si wonaa Kanko."
  18,28,"Tabintin wonkii maa kin e wonndinagol e …ìen noddoo…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe noddaandu dewal e noddaandu toraare ka arannde √±allal e ka sakkitorde maggal, ko a la…ì…ìinan…óo Mo, wata a yawtin …ìe gite maa…óen, faale…óaa joo…óodugol e yim…ìe anndiraa…ìe ngalu e hooreyaagal, wata a tewto on mo Men wa…ói …ìernde mun nden welsindii nde e jantagol Men sabu ko men uddi nde kon, sakko o yamire ha…óugol …ìillii…ìe …ìen ka mbatu maa, o ardini jokkugol ko welata kon wonkii makko e dow doftagol Joomi makko, golle makko …óen laatii yeebii…óe."
  18,29,"Maakan -an Nulaa…óo- …ìee derfu…ìe=fijoobe e jantagol Alla sabu welsindaare …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe: ""Ko mi addani on kon ko Goonga, …óun ko immorde ka Alla wonaa immorde e an, mi jaabotaako ko noddu…óon lan kon e mun fii yo mi ra…óo gom…óin…ìe …ìen. Kala yi…óu…óo e mo'on gom…óinngol kaa Goonga yo o gom…óin ka, aray ka o weltoroya njoddi mun ndin, kala yi…óu…óo e mo'on yeddugol …óun yo o yeddu, aray ka o tampiroya lepte habbii…óe mo …óen"". Menen Men heblanii too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen subagol geddi=keefaraagal Yiite mawnge pette magge …óen no hunnditi …ìe, …ìe hattantaake dogugol nge, si …ìe …óa…ì…ìii faaboreede ndiyan sabu sattude …óonka ka …ìe hawri e mun, …ìe faaboree ndiyan wa'u…óa wa nebban taynaa…óa hattu…óan wulugol, …óan ju…óa geece ma…ì…ìe …óen sabu sattude nguli, …óan njaram …óan …ìe faaboraa …óun, bonii njaram, …óan ittataa …óonka, ko woni …óan …ìeyday ka, …óan √±ifataa ngen yiite wonnge √±aamude guri ma…ì…ìe, Yiite ngen bonii werde nde …ìe wernetee e mun, e √±ii…ìirde nde …ìe √±ii…ìata e mun."
  18,30,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óin…ìe Alla …ìe golli golleeji mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, gom…óii …ìe labinii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen no woodani …ìe mbarjaari mawndi, Menen Men yeebataa njoddi kala mo∆¥∆¥in…óo golle, ko woni Men huubinanay …ìe njoddiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin ko …ói timmu…ói hara …ói uytaaka."
  18,31,"∆Åen siforaa…ìe gom…óinal …ìe golli golleeji mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, no woodani …ìe Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal hi…ìe √±ii…ìa nderton poomaa, can…ói Aljanna welu…ói …óin no ila ka ley galleeji ma…ì…ìe. Hi…ìe cu…óiree nder ton mulle=jawe kan≈ãe, …ìe …ìornoo conci haaki…óu…ói immorde e …óewlu…ói =hariire e tekku…ói mun, hi…ìe so…ì…ìindoo e dan…óe cu…óiraa…óe wirngallooji=ridooji labaa…ói, mbarjaari ma…ì…ìe ndin mo∆¥∆¥ii, Aljanna on mo∆¥∆¥ii werde e √±ii…ìirde nde …ìe √±ii…ìata e muu…óun."
  18,32,"Fiyu misal -an Nulaa…óo- fii wor…ìe …ói…óo: Keefeero e gom…óin…óo, Men wa…óani keefeero on e ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo gese …ói…ói, Men howiri gese …óen …ói…ói da∆¥∆¥i tamaro, Men fu…óini ka yannji heneere majje remuruuji."
  18,33,"Ngesa kala rimi ndim…óe mabba immorde e tamaro e inabu e remuru, mba uytaali hay e huunde, ko woni mba okkir …óun no huu…ìiri e no timmiri, Men ilini hakkunde majje caangol fii yarnirgol …óe no newori."
  18,34,"Laatanii jey…óo gese …óen …ói…ói jawle e dim…óe goo, o wi'ani wonndii…óo makko gom…óin…óo on tawi himo yewtude mo fii yo o battin e makko ko o hoditii…óo: ""Min mi…óo …ìurumaa jawle, mi…óo …ìurumaa teddude ban≈ãe e tii…óude gorol""."
  18,35,"Keefeero on naati ka ngesa makko himo wonndi e gom…óin…óo on fii yo o hollu mo mba, tawi himo too√±iri hoore-makko keeferaaku e hawtaare, keefeero on wi'i: ""Mi sikkaa mbaa ngasa mba suti…óaa+ndaarataa …óoo lannay; sabu ko mi wa…óani mba kon e sababuuji heddagol""."
  18,36,"Mi sikkaa Darngal ngal wa…óay, pellet, …óa'an ko ngurndan duumii…óan, si tawii le ngal daroyi si mi immintinaama mi artiraama ka Joomi an, mi he…ìay …ìaawo immital ngal ko mi ruttoo e mun, huunde …ìurunde mbaa ngesa an. Wonugol an galo ka aduna …óoo …óun no holli nde mi wonoyta galo …ìaawo immital ngal."
  18,37,"Wonndii…óo makko gom…óin…óo on tawi himo ruttannde mo haala kan o wi'i mo: ""Enee a yeddii On Tagu…óo baaba maa…óa Aadama e mbullaari, refti O Tagumaa an e maniiyu, refti O wa…óumaa ne…ó…óanke gorko, O fonni tere maa…óen O wa…óumaa timmu…óo, awa On Hattan…óo e dow …óii…óoo fow ko O Hattan…óo immintinngol ma""."
  18,38,"Kono min mi wi'ataa ngool kongol maa …óoo, anndu ko mi wi'ata: Kanko Alla Senayee wonanii Mo Joomi an ∆Åurnir…óo Neemaaji Makko …óin e amen, mi kafidataa=renndintaa Mo hay e gooto ka Dewal."
  18,39,"Hanno tuma nde naatu…óaa ka ngesa maa…óa wi'aa: ""Ko Alla muuyi kon doole alanaa hay gooto si wanna Alla, ko Kanko woni wa…óoowo ko O faalaa ko Kanko woni Dolnu…óo, si a wonii ndaara mi…óo …ìurumaa …ìillaade e fan…óude …ìi…ó…ìe."
  18,40,"Min mi…óo tijjii nde Alla okkinmi mo∆¥∆¥ore …ìurnde ngesa maa mban, e nde O nulata e ngesa maa mban lepte immorde ka kammu, ngesa maa…óa mban wonta leydi ndi pu…ói alaa e mun hara teppe mortoto e mayri sabu …ìowrugol mayri."
  18,41,"Maa…óun ndiyan mabba …óan ila muta ka nder leydi, hara a hattantaake yottorgol e majjan wallitorkun, si ndiyan mabba …óan mutii hara heddagol alanaa …óan."
  18,42,"Ko gom…óin…óo on tijjinoo kon halkuyee=halkaare huu…ìiti dim…óe ngesa keefeero on,keefeero on wattini himo waylita newe makko …óen ka sattude suno e nimse e dow ko o rokki kon jawle fii dankagol mba e mo∆¥∆¥inngol mba, ngesa mban ko yanumba e hoore tugaale mun, …óen …óe cal…ói inabuuje …óen layi hoore mun,himo wi'a: ""Ee jalla wonno min,mi gom…óinno Joomi an Kanko Tun, hara mi kafidaano e Makko hay e gooto e jeyaa…ìe …ìen."
  18,43,"Laatanaaki oo keefeero jamaa walloo…ìe mo immorde e lepte jippii…óe e makko …óen, ko kanko non wonnoo wasorde jamaa, kanko o laataaki sakkotoo…óo Alla e halkugol ngesa mban."
  18,44,"No e nder nden darorde Ballal Alla ngal Kanko tun, ko Kanko Senii…óo On woni Mo∆¥∆¥u…óo mbarjaari wonannde yi…ó…ìe Makko gom…óin…ìe …ìen, ko Kanko sowanta …ìe mbarjaari ndin, e Mo∆¥∆¥o battane wonannde …ìe."
  18,45,"An Nulaa…óo, piyan …ìen hoditor…ìe aduna misal, yeru ngurndan aduna e nattingol mun e yaawude lannude mun ko yeru ndiyan to…ìo, …óan Men jippini …óun immorde ka kammu, fu…óiri sabu …óan ndiyan pu…ói leydi ndin …ói …ìenndi, …óin pu…ói wonti helu…ói muncii, keneeli …óin no ronndoo kuntoy majji na…ìira e ban≈ãeeji goo, leydi ndin ruttoo no ndi wonirnoo, Alla yen…óii ko O Hattan…óo e dow kala huunde, huunde ronkintaa Mo, hiMo wurna ko O yi…ói, O re'a ko O yi…ói."
  18,46,"Jawdi ndin e …ìi…ó…ìe …ìen …óun no jeyaa e ko cu…óortee ka ngurndan aduna, jawdi alaa nafa ka laahara si wanaa si ndi golliraama e huunde weltinaynde Alla, golle …óen e konngu…ói yarlaa…ói …óin ka Alla …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude mbarjaari immorde e kala ko woni kon ka aduna e cu…óaaje, ko …óin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko ne…ó…óanke on yelotoo …óun; sabu cu…óaari aduna lannay mbarjaari golle …óen e konngu…ói yarlaa…ói …óin ka Alla ko heddotoondi."
  18,47,"Janto √±annde Men ittata pelle …óen e fudirde majje, a yi'ay leydi ndin ko fee√±undi sabu iwugol ko woni kon e hoore mayri immorde e pelle e le…ó…óe e maadiiji, Men moo…ìa denndaangal tageefooji …óin, Men accataa hay e gooto e ma…ì…ìe si wanaa Men immintinii mo."
  18,48,"Yim…ìe …ìen wee…ìitee ka Joomi maa ko …ìe saffeeji O hasba …ìe, wi'anee …ìe: ""Gm…óii on arii ka Amen gooto gooto hol…ìe solii…ìe wano Men tagirnoo on non ka laawol aranol, ko woni, on aa∆¥ino wonnde onon on immintintaake, wonnde Menen Men wa…óanaano on jamaanu e nokkuure nde Men yo…ìata on e mu'un golleeji mo'on …óin""."
  18,49,"Deftere golleeji nden wallinee, no woodi nanngiroowo deftere mun √±aamo mun ngon, no woodi kadi nanngiroowo nde nano mun ngon, a yi'ay -an ne…ó…óanke- heefer…ìe …ìen ko hulu…ìe ko woni kon e mayre; sabu kam…ìe hi…ìe anndi ko …ìe ardini kon e nder mayre immorde e keeferaaku e geddi, …ìi wi'a: ""Ee halakuyee amen e nammbara amen! ko he…ìi ndee deftere nde accataa ko fan…ói wanaa ko njan…ói e golle amen si wanaa nde limii …óun nde marii"". ∆Åe tawa ko …ìe golle kon ka ngurndan ma…ì…ìe aduna immorde e geddi ko winndaa…óun tabintinaa, Joomi maa…óa too√±ataa -an Nulaa…óo- hay e gooto, O leptataa hay e gooto ko aldaa e bakkaatu, O ustantaa …óoftii…óo on e mbarjaari …óoftaare makko nden hay e huunde."
  18,50,"Janto -an Nulaa…óo- fewndo Men wi'annoo Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen: ""Sujjanee Aadama sujjannde hiwraango, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe …ìe sujjani mo ka …óoftaade Yamaruyee Joomi ma…ì…ìe si wonaa Ibliisa o laatii jeyaa…óo e jinnaaji …óin o wonaali jeyaa…óo e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen, o salii o mawnintinanii sujjugol ngol, o yalti e …óoftaari Joomi makko. Enee, on jogitoto mo -ko onon yo yim…ìe- kanko e …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen yi…ó…ìe …ìe weldon e mun gaanin An, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe a√±u…ìe on. Ko honno jogitorton ay…ìe mon …ìen yi…ó…ìe mon?! Kaanii bonii golle too√±oo…ìe …ìen …ìen wa…óu…ìe seytaane gi…óo ma…ì…ìe mbattude weldugol e Alla O toowii."
  18,51,"∆Åe'e, …ìe jogiti…óon …óun yi…ó…ìe gaanin An, …ìen ko jeyaa…ìe yeruu…ìe mo'on, Mi hollaano …ìe Tagugol kammuuli …óin wanaa Tagugol leydi ndin kadi fewndo Mi Tagaynoo…ói, ko woni, hari …ìe wonaali woodaa…ìe, Mi hollaano yoga ma…ì…ìe kadi Tagugol yoga, ko Min woni Weddor…óo Tagugol ngol e Fewjugol ngol, Mi wonaali kadi jogitotoo…óo majjinoo…ìe …ìen immorde seytanuuji yim…ìe e jinna walloo…ìe, Min Mi…óo Yonndinii e walloo…ìe …ìen."
  18,52,"Jantano …ìe -an Nulaa…óo- √ëalnde Darngal tuma nde Alla Daalanta …ìen sirkannoo…ìe Mo ka aduna: ""Noddee kafidaa…ìe An …ìen, …ìen …ìe aa∆¥ino…óon wonnde kam…ìe ko …ìe kafidaa…ìe An bela-jo'o kam…ìe …ìe wallay on, …ìe nodda …ìe …ìe noototaako noddaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun …ìe wallataa…ìe, Men wa…óa hakkunde rewoo…ìe …ìen e rewaa…ìe …ìen halkorde nde …ìe kafi e mun, …óun ko Yiite Jahannama."
  18,53,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen yi'a Yiite ngen, …ìe yananee hattirde e yananeede wonnde kam…ìe …ìe yanay e nder magge, …ìe he…ìantaa nge nokkuure nde …ìe sellirta =pirlitorto e mun."
  18,54,"Gom…óii Men …ìannginii Men nooninii e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare Telliinde e dow Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko O hisina mo) ko …óuu…ói e nooneeji mise fii yo …ìe annditu …ìe waajitoo, kono ne…ó…óanke on -tentinii keefeero on- himo …ìuri kala huunde nde wennje …óe aldaa e goonga fee√±ata e mun."
  18,55,"Heedaali hakkunde heefer…ìe sanndal…óii…ìe …ìen e gom…óinngol ko Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko O hisina mo) addi kon immorde e Joomi makko, heedaali hakkunde ma…ì…ìe e …óa…ì…ìugol haforaneede junubaaji=bakkatuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin ka Alla ustagol …ìannginngol. Gom…óii mise …óen piyanaama …ìe ka nder Alqur'aana, hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói ari e ma…ì…ìe, anndu, ko ha…ói …ìe ko …óa…ì…ìugol -no tii…óiri- yanugol lepte moftaaji fe∆¥∆¥u…ói …óin e hoore ma…ì…ìe, e yi'ugol lepte …ói …ìe fodaa …óen."
  18,56,"Men Nuliraali …ìen …ìe Men Nuli immorde e Nulaa…ìe Amen si wanaa ko …ìe weltinoo…ìe yim…ìe gom…óinal ngal e …óoftaare nden, e hul…ìinoo…ìe yim…ìe keefeeru ngun e geddi …óin, alanaa …ìe wurtagol e hoore …ìer…óe …óen fii fawugol …óe e hoore Peewal ngal, …ìen yeddu…ìe Alla e Nulaa…ìe …ìen no wennja wonndude e fee√±anngol …ìe dalil on, fii yo …ìe ittir meere ma…ì…ìe nden Goonga Tellinaa…óo on e Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko O hisina mo) …ìe watti Alqur'aana on e ko …ìe hul…ìiniraa kon samakal e jalnori=jalnirde."
  18,57,"Alaa hay e gooto …ìur…óo sattude too√±e ko foti e on waajuraa…óo Aayeeje Joomi makko …óen, tawi o haajaaka ko woni kon e nder majje immorde e kammbaa lepte …óen, o …óuurii e waajitorgol …óe, o yejjeti ko o ardini kon ka ngurndan makko aduna immorde e keeferaaku e geddi o tuubaali e majji, Menen Men wa…óii e …ìer…óe …ìen ko muurata ha…óa …óe immorde e faamugol Alqur'aana on, e ka noppi ma…ì…ìe kadi pahu gaayi …óun, …ìe nanataa nde nan…óe ja…ìugol, hay si a noddii …ìe e gom…óinal …ìe jaabotaako ko noddataa …ìe kon e mun poomaa fodde no ka …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe coddu, e ka noppi ma…ì…ìe pahu."
  18,58,"Fii wata Annabiijo on (yo Alla juulu e makko O hisina mo) yollitu faade e ko fennu…ìe …ìen hawjirta kon lepte …óen, Alla Daalani mo: ""Ko Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- woni Surroowo bakkatuuji jeyaa…ìe Makko tuubu6 …ìe …ìen, ko O Jom Yurmeende, nden yaajannde kala huunde, no jeyaa e Yurmeende Makko nden wonnde Kanko O nennanay yeddu…ìe …ìen bela-jo'o kam…ìe …ìe tuubay …ìe ruttoto e Makko, sinndo Kanko O toowii, O leptayno …ìee …óuurii…ìe O yaccinanayno …ìe lepte …óen ka ngurdan aduna, kono Kanko ko O Mun√±ii…óo Yurmitee…óo, O nennane …ìe lepte …óen fii yo …ìe tuubu, ko woni, no woodani …ìe nokkuure e jamaanu happaa…ói …ói…ói …ìe yo…ìoyte e mayre keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun e …óuuragol ma…ì…ìe ngol si tawii …ìe tuubaali, …ìe he…ìataa gaanin mayre fattorde nde …ìe fattoo e mun."
  18,59,"∆äen ca'e yeddu…óe …ìadii…óe on, yeru ca'e yim…ìe Huudu e Saalihu e su'aybu Men halkuno …ìe nde …ìe too√±irnoo ko'e-ma…ì…ìe keefeeraaku e geddi, Men wa…óani halkugol …ìe ngol waqtu happaa…óo."
  18,60,"Janto -an Nulaa…óo- nde Muusaa (yo o his) maakanno kurkaadu makko ndun Yuusa'u ge…óal Nuun: ""Mi seerataa mi…óo yaha haa mi hewta fottirde maaje …óen …ói…ói, maa…óun mi yaha jamaanu juutungu haa mi fotta e jeyaa…óo mo∆¥∆¥u…óo on, mi jannga e makko."
  18,61,"∆Åe yahi, nde …ìe hewtoynoo fottirde maaje …óen …ói…ói …ìe yejjiti linngii ma…ì…ìe ngii, ngin ngi …ìe jogitii …óun njoo…ìaari ma…ì…ìe, Alla wurniti linngii ngii, ngii jogitii laawol ka maayo yeru wuddere, ndiyan …óan heewataa e mun."
  18,62,"Tuma nde …ìe hewtoynoo nden nokkuure, Muusaa (yo o his) maakani kurkaadu makko ndun: ""…ìannanii en so∆¥∆¥aari ndin, gom…óii en hawrii immorde e ndu'u yaadu men tampere sattunde."
  18,63,"Suka on wi'i: ""A yi'ii ko wa…ói kon fewndo soruno…óen ka fetere?! Min mi yejjituno anndintinngol ma fii linngii ngin, yejjintinaali lan anndintinngol ma fii maggin si wonaa Seytaane, gom…óii linngii ngin wuuritii, laawol wa…óanaa ngin ka maayo hingii yahira no hawnori."
  18,64,"Muusaa (yo o his) maakani kurkaadu makko ndun: ""ko …óon ko faala…óen kon woni, ko …óun woni maande nokkuure jeyaa…óo mo∆¥∆¥o on, …ìe yiltitii hi…ìe jokka batte teppe ma…ì…ìe …óen; fii wata …ìe majju laawol ngol haa …ìe hewtoya ka fetere, immorde …óon haa ka naatirde linngii ngin."
  18,65,"Tuma nde …ìe hewtoynoo nokku ka …ìe hattii linngii ngin …óon, …ìe tawi …óon jeyaa…óo immorde e jeyaa…ìe Amen mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe, (on ko Khadiru, yo o his) Men Okkii mo Hinnayee immorde e Amen, Men anndini mo immorde e Amen Ganndal yim…ìe …ìen ∆¥ellitaaki e maggal, ko …óun oo fillayee …óoo mofti."
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo e hoore yankinaare e newaare: ""Enee a accay mi jokke fii yo a anndinan yoga e ko Alla anndin maa e Ganndal ngal ka√±un ko Peewal faade e Goonga kan?"
  18,67,"Khadiru maaki: ""Pellet, an a waawataa mun√±aande e kon ko yi'ataa …óun immorde e ganndal an; sabu …óun hawrondiraa ko woni kon ka maa…óa immorde e ganndal."
  18,68,"Ko honno mun√±urtaa e dow …óun ko yi'ataa e golleeji …óin …ói a anndaa senngo feewungo ngon e majji; sabu an ko √±aawirtaa e majji ko emmbere ganndal maa ngal?"
  18,69,"Muusaa maaki: ""Si Alla Muuyii, a taway lan ko mi mun√±ii…óo e dow ko mi yi'ata kon immorde e maa…óa e golleeji, ko mi tabitu…óo e doftagol ma, mi yeddataa yamaruyee maa mo yamir…óaa mi …óun""."
  18,70,"Khadiru maakani Muusaa: ""Si a jokkay lam, wata lanndo lam fii huunde e ko yi'ataa kon mi…óo wa…óa haa tawa ko min woni fu…ó…óotoo…óo on …ìannginngol kene mayre""."
  18,71,"Tuma nde …ìe fottanno e …óum, …ìe yahi ka fonngo maayo haa …ìe hawri e laana, …ìe bakii e makka …ìe yo…ìaali sabu teddinngol Khadiru, Khadiru tufiri laana kan …ìurugol peccal e pecce makka, Muusaa maakani mo: ""A tufii laana kan, kan ka yim…ìe mun baki en e nder mun ko aldaa e yo…ìugol, tijjagol ka yoolay yim…ìe makka …ìen?! Gom…óii a addii fiyaake maw…óo""."
  18,72,"Khadiru maakani Muusaa: ""Enee mi wi'aano: pellet, an a hattantaake mu√±al wonndugol e an e ko yi'ataa kon immorde e am""."
  18,73,"Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Khadiru: ""Wata a nanngitiran sabu …óalirgol an aadi maa ndin gejji, wata a …ìittinanan sattinaa ka wonndinagol e ma'a."
  18,74,"∆Åe hucciti …ìaawo jippagol ma…ì…ìe ka laana hi…ìe yaha ka fonngo, …ìe yi'i suka mo hellifaaka no fijida e sukaa…ìe, Khadiru wari mo, Muusaa maakani mo: ""E a waru wonkii laa…ìuki ki hellifaaka ki aldaa e bakkaatu woo?! Gom…óii a addii muraadu a√±aandu!""."
  18,75,"Khadiru wi'ani: Mussaa (yo o his): Min hari mi wi'iino ma: ""pellet, an -Muusaa- a hattantaake mu√±al e dow fiyaake ko mi wa…óata kon""."
  18,76,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: ""Si mi lanndike fii huunde …ìaawo ngol laawol …óoo haray seedu e an, haray gom…óii a hewtii e nokku mo ngantu mo accata fii wonndugol e an; sabu lunndagol an yamiroore maa…óa laabi tati."
  18,77,"∆Åe yahi haa …ìe hewti e yim…ìe saare …ìe …óa…ì…ìiri yim…ìe mayre …ìen √±aametee, yim…ìe saare nden salii √±amminngol …ìe, e tottugol e ma…ì…ìe hakkee wernugol, …ìe tawi ka saare maade wo√±iindi …ìattii-ndi yanugol yirba, Khadiru wurti ndi haa ndi feewi, Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Khadiru: ""Sinno a yi…óii ∆¥ittugol njoddi fii mo∆¥∆¥intingol ndi a ∆¥ettayno …óum; sabu katonnjinal me'en e …óum …ìaawo salagol ma…ì…ìe wernugol en."
  18,78,"Khadiru maakani Muusaa: ""Ngool falagol …óoo sabu anngal ∆¥ettugol njoddi fii wurtugol maadi ndin ko …óum woni nokku seedigal ngal hakkunde an e ma'a, aray mi humpite firo kon ko a hattananooka mun√±aade e dow mun e ko yi'u…óaa kon mi…óo wa…óa …óum."
  18,79,"Si ko kan laana ka yeddir…óaa mi sabu yulugol ka; hari ka wonanii lo'u…ìe hi…ìe gollera ka ka maayo …ìe hattantaake hiwugol ka, mi faalaa ko mi wa…ói kon e makka yo wontan ka ayyibe; fii wata halor ka lam…óo won…óo yeeso ma…ì…ìe on, on ja…ìtoowo kala laana mo∆¥∆¥uka e junngo jom makka, o …óala kala laana wonnduka e ayiiibe."
  18,80,"Si ko on suka mo yeddir…óaa lam sabu warugol mo neene makko e baaba makko laatike gom…óim…ìe, tawi kanko e Ganndal Alla ko o keefeeru, men huli si o hellifaama wata o ukku…ìe e yeddugol Alla e bewre sabu fantude giggol ma…ì…ìe e makko, maa…óun sabu fantude katojinal ma…ì…ìe e makko."
  18,81,"Men faalaa yo Alla lontinan…ìe …ìi…ó…óo …ìur…óo mo mo∆¥∆¥ude Diina e laa…ìal immorde e bakkaatu, e …ìur…óo …ìadaade yurmeende jibin…ìe …ìen …ói…óo."
  18,82,"Si ko ndin maadi ndi mi mo∆¥∆¥ontini …óum yeddu…óaa mi e mo∆¥∆¥intingol ndi, ko fii cukaloy …ói…óo koy baaba mun maayi no ka saare nde aru…óen e mu'un, tawi jawdi no iranaa koy ka ley maadi, baaba koy cukaloy …ói…óoy laatino ne…ó…óo mo∆¥∆¥o, Joomi maa…óa faalaa -an Muusaa- yo …ìe mawnu …ìe hewtu duu…ìi peewal, …ìe yaltina jawdi ma…ì…ìe iraandi ndin ka ley maadi; sinno maadi ndin yanuno jooni jawdi ma…ì…ìe ndin yaltitayno ndi wee…ìitanoo yeebagol, ndee e…ì…ìoore …óoo laatike Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa nde O Yurmaa…ìe, mi wa…óiraali …óum immorde e tinnaare am, …óum ko firo ko a hattanaaka mun√±aade e dow mun kon."
  18,83,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen e Alyahuuda en no lanndaade ma -an Nulaa…óo- e ndarndagol fii kumpital jom gaLlaa…ói …óin …ói…ói, maaku: ""Arma mi janngana on see…óa e kumpital fii makko ko taskoron …óum waajito…óon""."
  18,84,"Menen Men wee…ìinanii mo ka leydi, Men Jonni mo e kala huunde nde o …óa…ì…ìata laawol hewtinayngol mo e faandaare makko."
  18,85,"O nanngi ko Men Okki mo kon immorde e laawi fii hewtugol e …óa…ì…ìaande makko, o sutori hirnaange."
  18,86,"O yahi ka leydi haa o hewti ka hattirde leydi ndin ka hella mutirde naange, o yi'i nge awiima kannge hinge muta e caangol wulungol wonndungol e loope …ìaleeje, o tawi ka mutirde naange ngen yim…ìe heefer…ìe, Men wi'ani mo e hoore su…ìinngol mo: ""Ko an yo jom galaa…ói …ói…ói, ko si a leptiray …ìee warugol maa tanaa mun, maa…óun si a mo∆¥∆¥oto e ma…ì…ìe."
  18,87,"Jom gallaa…ói …óin …ói…ói wi'i: ""Si tawii ko on sirkan…óo Alla o deppitii(doonii) e sirku ngun …ìaawo men noddii mo e dewal, men leptiray mo ka aduna warugol, refti o ruttoo ka Joomi makko √ëalnde Darngal O Lepta mo Lepte hul…ìinii…óe""."
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gom…óin…óo e ma…ì…ìe Alla o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i no woodani mo Aljanna; njo…ódi immorde ka Joomi makko sabu gom…óinal makko ngal e golle makko mo∆¥∆¥e …óen, aray Men wi'ana mo e fiyaake Amen ko wonndi e newaare."
  18,89,"Refti o jokki laawol tanaa laawol makko aranol ngol ko o fewtir…óo hella funnaange."
  18,90,"O yahi haa nde o hewtoynoo e nokkuure nde naange ngen ∆¥ellitotoo e mun, o tawi naange ngen no ∆¥ellitoo e dow yim…ìe Men wa…óanaali …ìe gaanin naange ngen ko hiwata …ìe wano cuu…ói e …óowdiiji le…ó…óe."
  18,91,"Ko wano nii fiyaake jom gallaa…ói …óin …ói…ói, gom…óii o fiiltiima ganndal e fennsitale ko woni kon ka makko e doole e laamu."
  18,92,"Refti o jokki laawol tanaa laawi arani …óin …ói…ói ko o falor…óo hakkunde funnaange e hirnaange."
  18,93,"O yahi haa o hewti yolnde hakkunde pelle …ói…ói, o tawi fewndo mayre yim…ìe …ìe mee…óaa faamude haala wo…ì…ìe goo."
  18,94,"∆Åe wi'i: ""Ko an Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja (…ìen ko moftaaji …ói…ói maw…ói e …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama) hi…ìe bonirde ka leydi ko …ìe woni wa…óude kon immorde e warngo e tanaa mun. Taw si men wa…óante jawdi fii yo a wa…óu hakkunde e ma…ì…ìe heedo?"""
  18,95,"Julqarnayni wi'i: ""Ko Joomi am arsiki lam kon e laamu e doole …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde lam diini gaa ko jonnoton lam e jawdi, walliree lam wor…ìe e aalaaji mi wa…óa hakkunde mo'on e ma…ì…ìe heedo""."
  18,96,"Addee kunte njam…óe, …ìe addi …óum o nanngi mahirgol …óe hakkunde pelle …óen …ói…ói, haa nde o feppindirirnoo hakkunde majje maadi makko ndin o wi'ani golloo…ìe …ìen: ""Hu…ì…ìinee yiite e dow …óe'e kunte, haa nde kunte njam…óe …óen wojjunoo o wi'i: ""Addee sila mi yuppa e dow mun."
  18,97,"Yaajuuja e Maajuuja hattantaake ∆¥awugol e hoore maadi ndin sabu toowugol mayri, …ìe hattantaake kadi tufugol ka ley mayri sabu yoorugol mayri."
  18,98,"Julqarnayni wi'i: ""Ngoo heedo ko Yurmeende immornde ka Joomi am nde no heeda hakkunde Yaajuuja e Maajuuja e bonnugol ka leydi, ngo ha…óa …ìe e …óum, si waqtu mo Alla happi on fii yaltugol ma…ì…ìe ado dargol Darngal ngal arii O wattinay ngo feppondirngo e leydi ndin, Fodoore Alla nden fii feppindirgol ngo e leydi ndin e yaltugol Yaajuuja e Maajuuja laatike ko tabitu…óum lurral alaa e mu'un""."
  18,99,"Men acca wo…ì…ìe e tagu ngun ka sakkitoode jamaanu ngun no ukkondira jillondira e wo…ì…ìe, alaadu ndun wuttee Men moo…ìi tagu ngun kala maggu fii hasboore nden e njo…ìde ndin."
  18,100,"Men fen√±inanay Jahannama yeddu…ìe …ìen fen√±inngol ngol aldaa e ji…ìayee fii yo …ìe seedo nge gite."
  18,101,"Men fen√±inana nge yeddu…ìe …ìen, …ìen laatinoo…ìe ko bum…ìe e jantagol Alla ka aduna; sabu ko woni kon ka gite ma…ì…ìe e wirngallo ha…óayngo …óum, …ìe laatii …ìe hattantaake nanugol Aayeeje Alla …óen nan…óe jabugol."
  18,102,"Enee …ìen yeddu…ìe Alla sikku …ìe wa…óay jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ìe e Nulaa…ìe e Seytanuuji rewetee…ìe gaanin Am?! Menen Men heblanii Jahannama fii yeddu…ìe …ìen galle fii werde ma…ì…ìe."
